The scene where Brian and Stewie walk in on Lois and Peter stoned and naked on the couch...on television, they're wearing underwear, on DVD they're fully nude.  The file in this torrent has them in underwear. And Lois does not say the line "Brian!  He's knockin at the back door!  Should I let him in?  I'm scared!".

Bums me out, that's one of my favorite Lois lines of all time.
